{"tid":1637999,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(好想扯旗) CCTV宣布停播NBA","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T07:42:12.000Z","uid":224375,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d1553cc3e8f0e17045d5914ee51701e8321425","tid":1637999,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"<ins>中央廣播電視總台央視體育頻道聲明</ins><br />\n<br />\n我們註意到正在日本參加活動的NBA總裁亞當&middot;肖華回應休斯敦火箭隊總經理莫雷發表涉港不當言論一事。對亞當-肖華聲稱支持莫雷自由表達權利的說辭，我們予以強烈不滿和反對。我們認為，任何挑戰國家主權和社會穩定的言論，不屬於該範疇。<br />\n<br />\n為此，中央廣播電視總台央視體育頻道決定，立即暫停NBA季前賽（中國賽）目前的轉播安排，立即排查涉及NBA的一切合作交流。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班大陸狗，留喺屋企睇CBA啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602da928426ea4a63a2a3dd7ca12b4a10e88ffd2","tid":1637999,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"季前賽"},{"pid":"f3e5b217e47dac142de0ccec9a72c48e0189e9d5","tid":1637999,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TIe8Rq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTIe8Rq1.jpg&h=afbe530c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"263b1c6f48707086532ed14bb199d437bca773ce","tid":1637999,"uid":59633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"翻牆睇正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a25317ba0bf667b7a3b0f2625ede4cbaaaf8350","tid":1637999,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:28:16.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</